{"tid":1472791,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【人手置頂】816機場 --- 聖詩班外國文宣組","createTime":"2019-08-14T16:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T02:42:29.000Z","uid":56052,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"55b10c068a4156656d2dbe2f72bef5e539319257","tid":1472791,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:13:36.000Z","msg":"上一個post 同大家解釋左點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都得到大部分人支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【公投】大家覺得如果我號召班基督徒嚟機場攞住文宣圖sing hallelujah 有冇得諗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470110\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470110</a></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，我決定號召一眾信徒，和<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">非信徒</span>一齊出嚟，用詩歌安撫機場旅客<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地道歉，係因為我地願意承擔所有行動嘅後果!<br />\n和理非繼續走出嚟，係因為不願同勇武手足割蓆!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n活動內容已經列喺channel 入面<br />\n816 機場聖詩文宣組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/christian816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fchristian816&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=d5640216\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/christian816</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請人手置頂，我地有組織得有d急，還請見諒</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家自己準備標語<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Yhf00J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Yhf00J.jpg&h=2b8e0981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o1ggLsp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo1ggLsp.jpg&h=91c5343f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yXJiYNq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyXJiYNq.jpg&h=80680ff4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"981184f70a6d8bc60c54ab835e12c83588849ddf","tid":1472791,"uid":56052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:14:09.000Z","msg